# CSS Variables System 2025

## Principi
- Palette estesa (HSL, P3)
- Adaptive theme: dark, high contrast, low light
- Uso di `@property` per custom properties animate
- Color-mix per varianti cromatiche
- Utility classes layer

## Esempi chiave

### Palette P3
```css
/* File: variables.css */
:root {
  /* Brand Palette */
  --brand-hue: 220;
  --brand-saturation: 85%;
  --brand-lightness: 60%;

  --brand-color: hsl(var(--brand-hue) var(--brand-saturation) var(--brand-lightness));
  --brand-color-p3: color(display-p3 0.23 0.35 0.76);

  /* Neutral Scale */
  --neutral-0: #ffffff;
  --neutral-100: #f5f7fa;
  --neutral-200: #e5eaf0;
  --neutral-300: #d5dde5;
  --neutral-400: #b7c2d0;
  --neutral-500: #8495a8;
  --neutral-600: #59697a;
  --neutral-700: #35404d;
  --neutral-800: #1f2833;
  --neutral-900: #0b121a;

  /* Semantic Colors */
  --success: hsl(145 72% 35%);
  --warning: hsl(36 92% 55%);
  --danger: hsl(355 80% 58%);

  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-color: 0 0 0 / 0.12;
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px var(--shadow-color);
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px var(--shadow-color), 0 2px 4px var(--shadow-color);
  --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px var(--shadow-color), 0 4px 6px var(--shadow-color);

  /* Typography */
  --font-sans: "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
  --font-serif: "Merriweather", "Georgia", serif;
  --font-mono: "Fira Code", monospace;

  /* Motion */
  --ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  --ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.45, 0, 0.55, 1);
}
```

### Adaptive Theme
```css
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --neutral-0: #0b121a;
    --neutral-100: #1f2833;
    --neutral-900: #ffffff;
  }
}

@media (prefers-contrast: more) {
  :root {
    --brand-lightness: 45%;
  }
}
```

### @property
```css
/* Definizione di --radius per contenerne i valori */
@property --radius {
  syntax: "<length>";
  inherits: false;
  initial-value: 0.5rem;
}

/* Example Usage */
.card {
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}
```

### Utility Layer
```css
@layer utilities {
  .text-primary {
    color: var(--brand-color);
  }
  .bg-primary {
    background-color: var(--brand-color);
  }
  .shadow-sm {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
}
```

